      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:32px;">Hurricane Pest Control — Your Questions Answered</h2>
      <div style="max-width:800px;">
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex serve Hurricane, Utah?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Yes. Wernex Termite & Pest Control regularly serves Hurricane and is just 20 minutes from the city center. We offer same-day inspections and emergency service for Hurricane residents. Call (435) 673-9503.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">What pests are most common in Hurricane, UT?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Hurricane's warm desert climate makes it a hot spot for scorpions, black widows, bark scorpions, fire ants, subterranean termites, and mice. The proximity to Sand Hollow and the Virgin River also increases mosquito activity during warmer months.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">How much does pest control cost in Hurricane?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Wernex offers free inspections and competitive pricing for Hurricane homeowners. Quarterly residential plans start at affordable rates, with no long-term contracts required. Call (435) 673-9503 for a free, no-obligation quote.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Does Wernex offer termite inspections in Hurricane?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Yes. Wernex provides WDI (Wood-Destroying Insect) inspections for Hurricane real estate transactions and homeowner peace of mind. We use Termidor advanced liquid barrier treatments for active infestations.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="reveal" style="background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;border:1px solid var(--gray-light);cursor:pointer;">
          <summary style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-dark);">Is Wernex pest control safe for pets and children?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.7;">Absolutely. Wernex uses an Integrated Pest Management (IPM) approach with eco-friendly, low-toxicity products. All treatments are EPA-compliant, and our technicians will advise on specific precautions for your household.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTERNAL LINKS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Explore More</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:24px;">Related Services &amp; Areas</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:16px;max-width:900px;">
        <a href="pest-control-southern-utah.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🛡️ Pest Control Across Southern Utah</a>
        <a href="index.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🏠 Wernex Home — St. George Pest Control</a>
        <a href="services.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🛠️ Full Service List</a>
        <a href="pest-control-washington-ut.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📍 Pest Control in Washington, UT</a>
        <a href="pest-control-ivins-ut.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📍 Pest Control in Ivins, UT</a>
        <a href="pest-control-laverkin-ut.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📍 Pest Control in LaVerkin, UT</a>
        <a href="termite-control-st-george.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🪵 Termite Control — St. George</a>
        <a href="scorpion-control-st-george.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🦂 Scorpion Control — Southern Utah</a>
        <a href="bed-bug-treatment-southern-utah.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">🛏️ Bed Bug Treatment</a>
        <a href="contact.html" class="reveal" style="display:block;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--off-white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--gray-light);font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;color:var(--green-light);transition:var(--transition);">📞 Schedule an Appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA BOTTOM -->
  <section class="section--dark" style="padding:60px 0;text-align:center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color:var(--white);">Hurricane Pest Problems? We're 20 Minutes Away.</h2>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:16px auto 28px;max-width:55ch;">Same-day inspections, eco-friendly treatments, and a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. Wernex has served Southern Utah for over 30 years.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Schedule Free Inspection</a>
        <a href="tel:+14356739503" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg" style="border-color:var(--lime);color:var(--lime);">📞 (435) 673-9503</a>
